(895, 'Hamza Rafiq', 'Rabaa Fathy', 'nabila.hussain78@gmail.com', '7970749948 ', 'بعت الرساله دي يوم 29 ابريل<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSalaam. Hamza’s madrasah has opened up again after being closed due to the pandemic. Unfortunately I will not be renewing the course after it has finished this time. I would like to thank you all for all your help and support over these months in teaching Hamza. May Allah swt reward you all for your efforts. <br />\r\nJazakallah khairun.<br />\r\nPlease could you tell me the last date of his lesson.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nلما قولتله ماتوقفش وقلل محاضرات بعت الرساله دي<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHe is going to mosque to learn now so is not stopping InShaAllah..just stopping online class with Eealim. He will continue to learn the Quran InShaAllah<br />\r\n<br />\r\nتم توقيفه', 'تم الاتصال', 'she is very busy and asked to call back after 2 hours will be at 4 pm eg {emad 9/5/21}<br />\r\nshe opened and listened then turned into a voice message {emad 18/8/21}<br />\r\nbad connection {emad 19/1/22}', 'asked to call back ', 1, '', '2021-04-29', NULL, NULL, NULL),
