(898, 'Aleena Uddin', 'Heba Tamer', 'rafiahuddin@gmail.com', '447526403808 - 447940300333', 'بعتت الرسائل دي<br />\r\n<br />\r\n Assalamu&#39;Alaikum. I hope you are all well Insha&#39;Allah <br />\r\nWould it be possible to cancel the lessons today and moving forward please? <br />\r\nI&#39;m sorry to have to come to this decision now, but after trying to practise with aleena for the last few weeks, j feel like this learning platform is maybe not to her current ability. I feel she would fare better with face-to-face interactive lessons, which I&#39;m hoping to enroll her into in the near future.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you for all of your help and please do pass our gratitude onto sister Hebe. Shes a credit to you all and aleena loved her time with her. Please keep us all in your prayers and pray that my aleena will be able to learn our deen to her fullest ability. Jazak&#39;Allah khair<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMy phone isn&#39;t currently accepting calls due to some speaker difficulties<br />\r\nYou can call my husband at +447940300333', 'تم الاتصال', 'he said that Aleena studies face to face and he wants to return his money as he paid last month and he may take one session only {emad 9/5/21}<br />\r\na lot of calls with no answer {emad 17/6/21}<br />\r\na lot of calls with no answer {emad 17/1/22}', 'refused to come back<br />\r\nno answer', 1, '', '2021-05-04', NULL, NULL, NULL),
